ot\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"his shoulders\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am OK with that.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mentally we are strong, I am strong, we will get through this together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old added: \\\"It is what it is.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was disappointed with the fans.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fans\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We talked on the field and asked ourselves: what do we need from each other?\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was worse than in the first game.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first game\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need each other on the field, the hugs, the cheering.\\\"\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"the hugs\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheering\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is not staying at the Olympic Village with his fellow competitors at his own request and will not conduct the usual post-match mixed zone interviews.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"his fellow competitors\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"his own request\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the usual post-match mixed zone interviews\", \"f